The efforts to mend Harry's relationship with his brother, the Duke of Cambridge, have so far been unsuccessful after the Duchess called Harry at his California home. “The issue is William and Harry are both overly stubborn, so there’s not much hope," the source said. However, the source added that Prince William "still feels the loss" of his brother, after Harry and his wife Meghan Markle quit the Royal Family more than two years ago. FOLLOW BELOW FOR UPDATES... 